<h2>Best time to visit Shimla / Best season to visit Shimla</h2>
<p>March to June is considered the best time to visit Shimla, as the climate is perfect and suitable for all age groups, so you can enjoy a trip to Shimla with your whole family without thinking about climate conditions.</p>

<h2>How to reach Shimla / Travel guide to Shimla</h2>

<p><strong>By Air</strong>- You can find a direct flight from Delhi to Shimla during the festive season. You can get flights to Chandigarh and then take a toy train from Kalka to Shimla or can choose volvo to Shimla.</p>

<p><strong>By Train</strong>- You can take train ticket from your city to Chandigarh and then Chandigarh to Kalka, which is the nearest railway station to Shimla.</p>

<p><strong>By Road</strong>- You can easily take bus or tempo traveler from Delhi and Chandigarh to Shimla</p>

